1. installer  https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdcommenter
2. usage
  <lead> stands for '\' by default
  <lead>cc    -- comment current line
  <lead>cu    -- uncomment
  <lead>ca    -- switch between /* */ and // style
  <lead> cs   -- beautiful comment
  <lead>cA    -- add comment at the end of line
  <lead>cu    -- cancel comment

  
3. add additional space right after "//", edit your .vimrc, add below line
   let g:NERDSpaceDelims=1
